reviewText: This is nothing more than a vanity project to feed this guy's Trump-sized ego.  I can't tell you the number of times I cringed or felt secondhand embarrassment whilst watching this disasterpiece.  TAX THE RICH!
So good! I couldn't be happier with my purchase. Rock on.

Mesmerizing!  Sir Ivan is a force of nature!  Vivid, sexy, colorful; provocative!  He is a charismatic man who surrounds himself with beautiful, fun-loving people.  He provides fantasy and excitement to all who enter his realm.  The opulence of his castle is something we can all admire and appreciate.
Sir Ivan is amazing and his parties are awesome!

From the beginning to end it was a fantasy we all want to live and this guy is doing it! I hope one day to explore that wild party at his castle, I mean the guy has a CASTLE!!!

Solid movie.
